resources.string: 1. Self-check the number of strokes once a day.
2. Record the time taken until the number of strokes reaches 10.
3. Press the Start button to display the start time of the start inspection.
4. Whenever you feel a movement, press the + button.(If incorrectly checked - press button to correct.)
5. Time and elapsed time are displayed when the total number of strokes is 10.
6. The total number of strokes can be changed in the upper right menu bar>set of the check screen.
